<inglise> Those arrangements shall include the definition of the conditions for authorisation, checks and the penalties to be applied in cases of irregularity. </inglise>
<eesti> Nimetatud kord h&otilde;lmab heakskiitmise tingimuste m&auml;&auml;ratlemist, kontrolle ning eeskirjade eiramise korral kohaldatavaid karistusi. </eesti>
<inglise> In the case of imports of hemp seed as referred to in the first subparagraph, the licence referred to in paragraph 1 shall be issued only where the authorised importer undertakes that the competent authorities will be presented, within the time limits and under the conditions defined by the Member State, with documents attesting that the hemp seed covered by the licence has undergone, within a period of less than 12 months from the date on which the licence is issued, one of the following operations: </inglise>
<eesti> Esimeses l&otilde;igus osutatud kanepiseemnete impordi korral antakse l&otilde;ikes 1 nimetatud litsents v&auml;lja &uuml;ksnes juhul, kui heakskiidetud importija kohustub liikmesriikide poolt m&auml;&auml;ratletud ajavahemiku jooksul ja tingimustel esitama p&auml;devatele asutustele dokumendid, millega t&otilde;endatakse, et v&auml;hem kui 12 kuu jooksul alates litsentsi v&auml;ljaandmise kuup&auml;evast on litsentsiga h&otilde;lmatud kanepiseemned l&auml;binud &uuml;he j&auml;rgmistest toimingutest: </eesti>
