<inglise> - re-export to a non-Community country. </inglise>
<eesti> - reeksport kolmandasse riiki. </eesti>
<inglise> However, if part of the hemp seed covered by the licence has not undergone one of the operations referred to in the previous subparagraph within the time limit of 12 months, the Member State may, at the request of the authorised importer accompanied by justification, extend that time limit by one or two periods of six months. </inglise>
<eesti> Kui osa litsentsiga h&otilde;lmatud kanepiseemnetest ei ole 12 kuu jooksul l&auml;binud &uuml;hte eelmises l&otilde;igus osutatud toimingut, v&otilde;ib liikmesriik heakskiidetud importija p&otilde;hjendatud taotluse korral seda t&auml;htaega &uuml;he v&otilde;i kahe kuuekuulise ajavahemiku v&otilde;rra pikendada. </eesti>
<inglise> The attestations referred to in the second subparagraph shall be drawn up by the operators who have carried out the operations and shall comprise at least the following information: </inglise>
